data.details: Discover, Invent, Explore! Learn about amazing women who made a huge impact on the world around us with their incredible inventions. Participate in hands-on experiments to find out how these awesome inventions came to be and what makes them work. Things might even get a little messy or explode! You never know what to expect when exploring inventions! This event costs $12 per girl.
